properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 17 at 3:23PM AKST until February 19 at 4:00AM AKST by NWS Anchorage, AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 6 inches
with locally higher amounts up to 10 inches along the Upper
Hillside expected.

* WHEN...From 3 PM Tuesday to 4 AM AKST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the evening commute.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Light snow is expected to develop early
afternoon before the afternoon commute.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

For the latest road conditions call 5 1 1 or visit
511.alaska.gov.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 PM TUESDAY TO 4 AM AKST WEDNESDAY
